name: Diplomats of the Sealed Mists
description: After losing many family members to decay and frailty within the Moribund Mists, those of the Diplomats of the Sealed Mists who made it out are strong. And certainly stronger than they look. They're also known for the lengths theyâ€™ll go to get their due. Over both injustice and insult. Now, after unfurling a cursed scroll and discovering secrets few others in Kharth know, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
